			<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en"><span dir="auto">Урок: Время суток</span></h1>
			<div id="bodyContent">
				<div id="contentSub"><div id="mw-revision-info">Revision as of 11:04, 10 March 2015 by <a href="/index.php?title=User:Animal4ik&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new mw-userlink" title="User:Animal4ik (page does not exist)">Animal4ik</a>  <span class="mw-usertoollinks">(<a href="/index.php?title=User_talk:Animal4ik&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="User talk:Animal4ik (page does not exist)">Talk</a> | <a href="/Special:Contributions/Animal4ik" title="Special:Contributions/Animal4ik">contribs</a>)</span></div><br />
				<div id="mw-revision-nav">(<a href="/index.php?title=%D0%A3%D1%80%D0%BE%D0%BA:_%D0%92%D1%80%D0%B5%D0%BC%D1%8F_%D1%81%D1%83%D1%82%D0%BE%D0%BA&amp;diff=prev&amp;oldid=12256" title="Урок: Время суток">diff</a>) <a href="/index.php?title=%D0%A3%D1%80%D0%BE%D0%BA:_%D0%92%D1%80%D0%B5%D0%BC%D1%8F_%D1%81%D1%83%D1%82%D0%BE%D0%BA&amp;direction=prev&amp;oldid=12256" title="Урок: Время суток">← Older revision</a> | Latest revision (diff) | Newer revision → (diff)</div></div>
